cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image annotation and detection using deep learning models.
2. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also likely as the paper involves training recurrent neural networks to describe the contexts of a detected disease.
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses various regularization techniques used to train the convolutional neural networks.
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image annotation and detection in a radiology dataset of chest x-rays.
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper involves using text reports to mine disease names and train the deep learning models.
